%C3%A0o-hoa-s%C4%A9-n%E1%BB%AF/author-uGACXgsnUhz8jzFM5wVyDw">Đào hoa sĩ nữ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-Khi%C3%AAm-%C3%8Dch/Kim-L%C4%83ng-thu-h%E1%BB%A9ng/poem-XBljLlXOzyI6kWN7rpRQsQ">Kim Lăng thu hứng - 金陵秋興</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-Khi%C3%AAm-%C3%8Dch/author-KdxnA4RirR7LsAi6oOaAoA">Tiền Khiêm Ích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-H%C3%A0m/K%E1%BB%B3-24/poem-ZdziiD87z59le_ECJTvTfA">Kỳ 24 - 其二十四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-H%C3%A0m/author-FUm0aTv6MMEhKSvKSGMoVA">Vũ Phạm Hàm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-t%E1%BB%91ng-Nghi%C3%AAm-c%C3%B4ng-nh%E1%BA%ADp-tri%E1%BB%81u-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-U4gwY6WrGziIZjt2_BVD4A">Phụng tống Nghiêm công nhập triều thập vận - 奉送嚴公入朝十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Tr%C3%BAc-chi-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-Hjj-OV9M_QZelHb-3Icr9Q">Trúc chi từ kỳ 4 - 竹枝詞其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br></div>	</div>
